short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Jeno - Your Smart Web Content Assistant

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Jeno is a powerful Chrome extension designed to enhance your browsing experience by allowing you to interact and generate content more effectively using AI. 

Whether you're a content creator, social media manager, or just someone who wants to get more out of the web, Jeno provides you with a suite of tools to help you engage with content in meaningful ways.

Jeno is designed to streamline your workflow, saving you time and effort by bringing powerful content generation and interaction tools directly to your browser.
